{
  "doc_id": "12636",
  "text": "As a result of this work OWL ontology transformation algorithm to rules (to the concept map, where rules are coded in a special form) was developed based on the ideas described in [CITATION_1] . Several OWL ontologies were found in the Web to evaluate correctness and performance of our transformation algorithm. As a result of evaluation of the transformation algorithm it was concluded that some mechanism for reducing the algorithm runtime was required. Thus, the importance of this research was expressed by the fact that this research influenced the structure of SWES.",
  "correct_citation": {
